  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0874637cabf445b44aa6cb3553862f49, type: 3}
  m_Name: Mulut_1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::PenyakitData
  tagBahagian: Mulut
  namaPenyakit: Stomatitis (Oral Ulcer)
  namaPenyakitEN: Stomatitis (Oral Ulcer)
  tahapRisiko: Tahap 2
  tahapRisikoEN: Level 2
  gambar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1b8da6392cf51ab418a0c650178c18cc, type: 3}
  isGraphic: 1
  punca: Pelbagai faktor (bakteria, virus, kulat, nutrisi lemah, trauma, stres, alahan,
    sistem imun lemah).
  simptom: Gusi sangat merah/bengkak dan berulser, lidah pucat, lelangit tidak normal.
    Kucing berliur melampau, sakit bila disentuh, mulut berdarah, dan kurang selera
    makan.
  tindakan: Diagnosis doktor haiwan melalui pemeriksaan fizikal.
  maklumatTambahan: Berbeza dari ulser biasa. Mulut berbau sangat busuk. Kucing berhenti
    membersihkan diri menyebabkan bulu bergumpal. Kucing mungkin menjatuhkan makanan
    atau menangis ketika makan sehingga hilang berat badan.
  puncaEN: Various factors (bacteria, virus, fungus, poor nutrition, trauma, stress,
    allergies, weak immune system).
  simptomEN: Severely red/swollen and ulcerated gums, pale tongue, abnormal palate.
    The cat drools excessively, is painful when touched, has a bleeding mouth, and
    has a reduced appetite.
  tindakanEN: Diagnosis by a veterinarian through a physical examination.
  maklumatTambahanEN: Different from a normal ulcer. The mouth has a very foul odor.
    The cat stops grooming itself, causing matted fur. The cat may drop food or cry
    while eating, leading to weight loss.
